c\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zkq1665702925290.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zkq1665702925290.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zkq1665702925290.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zkq1665702925290\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Assignments for Improved Performance\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zkq1665702925290__assignments_for_improved_performance_141412\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If many client processes access one server machine, both client and server might run out of memory. To avoid this problem and reduce the number of server processes started, make changes in the client assignment file:\n </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zkq1665702925290__li_d23297e1_d23298e1_d23299e1\">Remove the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SEARCH_DESCRIPTOR</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SEARCH_OBJECT</span> settings.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zkq1665702925290__li_d23300e1_d23301e1_d23302e1\">Make services (<span class=\"ph filepath\">*.svc</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">udesc.urr</span>, and <span class=\"ph filepath\">uobj.dol</span> available on the client instead of on the server.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zkq1665702925290__p_d46709e1_d46710e1_d46711e1\">To get a better overview of assignments for each server, change the assignment files as follows:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zkq1665702925290__li_d23303e1_d23304e1_d23305e1\">For the server assignment files, create separate assignment files for database, application server, and environment. For example: <span class=\"ph filepath\">database.asn</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">sasv.asn</span> and <span class=\"ph filepath\">env.asn</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zkq1665702925290__li_d23306e1_d23307e1_d23308e1\">In the client assignment file, update the UST for database actions to DBMS and for file access to SASV.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Assignments for Improved Performance Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Assignments for Improved Performance If many client processes access one server machine, both client and server might run out of memory. To avoid this problem and reduce the number of server processes started, make changes in the client assignment file: Remove the $SEARCH_DESCRIPTOR and $SEARCH_OBJECT settings. Make services ( *.svc , udesc.urr , and uobj.dol available on the client instead of on the server. To get a better overview of assignments for each server, change the assignment files as follows: For the server assignment files, create separate assignment files for database, application server, and environment. For example: database.asn , sasv.asn and env.asn In the client assignment file, update the UST for database actions to DBMS and for file access to SASV. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}